document_data.name: Trusk Rantyne
document_data.mainbody: '''Trusk Rantyne''' was the Gate Lord of [[Mreyelundar]] in [[1479 DR]].
document_data.Background: Trusk was a jeweler and the nominal lord of Mreyelundar. However, he had no real power because the city's true ruler was a [[thief]] named [[Narnorn]].
